data.description: SHORT-TERM Rentals Allowed! ALL NEW Appliances, TVs, Water Heater and Metal Roof in 2023! This home is the largest 2-story floor plan with a 2-car garage in the subdivision of Palm Cove, Panama City Beach, Florida. Homes in this subdivision have great STR income potential due to the amenities and location being south of HWY 98 and close to Shipwreck Island Water Park and the Miller County Pier!. This 3-bed/2.5bath home sits on a corner lot with a back patio overlooking the pond, and next to the kids playground. Open concept kitchen with all new stainless steel appliances and an expansive living area, attractively furnished and rental ready, this established vacation rental can easily accommodate up to 10-guests. All bedrooms are located upstairs plus a double bunk in the loft area. The master suite is spacious with a large walk-in closet and peaceful views to the pond. Palm Cove offers community pools, trash service, power washing, ground maintenance and security gates just a block from Shipwreck Island Waterpark and 2-blocks from Rock'it Lanes and several fine restaurants and attractions.. All Information is deemed to be reliable, but is not guaranteed, buyer to verify if important.
